WEBVTT

00:02.931 --> 00:05.239
Kyle: I don't think you understand
how big a mess we're in.

00:05.264 --> 00:07.247
My disability checks
are barely covering our bills,

00:07.272 --> 00:08.163
much less all of this.

00:08.188 --> 00:10.534
I got the most awesome job
at this spa in Sugar Land.

00:10.559 --> 00:11.803
Isn't that
like an hour away?

00:11.828 --> 00:14.204
Oh, trust me, honey. It's
so worth it. Tips are great.

00:14.229 --> 00:16.241
You can tell them I sent you
if you, uh, really need a job.

00:16.265 --> 00:17.482
I got the job.

00:17.507 --> 00:18.322
You hear that, kids?

00:18.347 --> 00:20.318
Mommy is the official
new breadwinner.

00:20.532 --> 00:21.926
Having some issues
with your shoulder?

00:21.951 --> 00:24.061
Uh, my hips and legs
are a little tight, too.

00:24.086 --> 00:25.346
Oh, okay.
I can take care of that.

00:25.371 --> 00:25.953
- Nice.
- Hey!

00:26.559 --> 00:28.096
You didn't think
it was important to tell me

00:28.121 --> 00:29.752
that the guys here
expect extras?

00:29.777 --> 00:32.107
90% of what we do here
is legit.

00:32.131 --> 00:33.909
I have a client list
for a few guys

00:33.934 --> 00:35.631
who like
a little something extra.

00:35.632 --> 00:38.634
Kyle left me, and I have no idea
if he's ever coming back.

00:38.669 --> 00:40.036
Kyle's been gone a while.

00:40.070 --> 00:42.271
It might be time
to let the house go.

00:42.306 --> 00:44.607
Their daddy's gone. I can't
take their house away, too.

00:44.641 --> 00:46.075
Riley: I need to make
more money here.

00:46.109 --> 00:47.443
Get me one of the guys
on the list.

